
General CC rules:

5 cards per 24 rolling months

5 hard inquiries per 24 rolling months

Keep minimum of 1 year average age of accounts.

Keep balance across all credit lines 15% utilization or lower

For most lenders, asking for more credit every 91 days is generally acceptable after account is 6 months - 1 year old.

Total credit lines can total up to 600% stated income if handled well. 

Don't close card immediately if after bonus offers.

